First Time User
Personal Online Banking
Your time is important to you and it’s equally important to Colony Bank. That’s why we created Colony Online Banking. It is designed for people with your lifestyle, who want to bank when and where it is convenient for them. And best of all, it is free. At your convenience, you will be able to:

View account balances
Transfer funds
Make Loan Payments
Check on status of deposits, loans, cleared checks, ATM transactions
View monthly account information for checking, money markets, savings, IRAs, loans and CDs
View and print current and previous period account statements – available in two formats; statement only or statement with check images like the one that is mailed to you
Download account activity into financial management software such as Quicken® or Microsoft Money®
Pay bills online

To sign up for Personal Online Banking, please click here.
Business Online Banking
Experience the convenience of Colony Business Online! Our new online banking system is especially designed to meet the needs of the business owner. There is no charge for the new system and it includes the following features:

The Ability to Control Account Access by Employee
Issue Stop Payments on Checks (Stop Payment Fee Applies)
Transfer Funds Between Accounts
Verify Account Balances
Review Account Activity
Download Account Activity
View and Print Check Images
Initiate ACH and Wire Transfer Transactions (Fee Applies, Coming this Summer)

To sign up for Business Online Banking, please click here to fill out all of the applications.






