			Company Description 


			Colony Bankcorp, Inc. operates as a bank holding company, which engages in the provision of financial services. It offers bill payments, mobile banking and deposit, cash management, telephone banking, merchant services, debit and credit cards, night depository, checking and savings accounts, preferr...
		


                Colony Bankcorp, Inc. operates as a bank holding company, which engages in the provision of financial services. It offers bill payments, mobile banking and deposit, cash management, telephone banking, merchant services, debit and credit cards, night depository, checking and savings accounts, preferred money market, working capital, loans, and mortgages. The company was founded on November 8, 1982 and is headquartered in Fitzgerald, GA.
            




